    <p>Visualize your goals and you will achieve them, that is the power of the human spirit!</p>
    <p>When you create a visual representation of your desires, it enlists your subconscious to creatively find ways to accomplish those goals.</p> 
    <p>Setting clear goals allows you to have a road map pointing to your desires, which will allow you to make educated decisions when you reach a metaphoric fork in the road.</p>
    <p>Finally, it helps to keep you motivated. If you are ready to begin, sign up - it's free and fun!</p>
    <p>A quick note from the author:</p>
    <blockquote>This might seem like a weird blend of hippie and materialistic idealogy, but I'm telling you it really helps to keep you on track. I created this project while working from home, where distractions abound, but after creating my sample vision board I noticed that I looked at my phone less, went to the kitchen for a snack less.  I had work to do, I still have work to do, and that is where I am, knocking out this project so someday, that Audi R8 will be in my garage and not just on my vision board.  Thanks for all of the support, and I hope this project helps you along your path.<author>Chris Thompson</author></blockquote>
